.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|[[Jared Rosholt]]\n|def.\n|[[Kelvin Tiller]]\n|Decision (unanimous) (20-18, 20-18, 20-18)\n|2\n|5:00\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Featherweight\n|[[Lance Palmer]]\n|def.\n|Max Coga\n|Decision (unanimous) (20-18, 20-18, 20-18)\n|2\n|5:00\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Featherweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|Mo De'Reese\n|def.\n|[[Mike Kyle]]\n|TKO (strikes)\n|1\n|2:38\n|2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs Alternate.\n}}\n{{MMAevent end|notes=yes}}\n\n==2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs==\n\n{{Round8\n<!-- Nothing/Fighter 1/Result 1/Fighter 2/Result 2 -->\n<!-- round of 8 -->\n||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Francimar Barroso]] (1)|L|{{flagicon|USA}} '''Josh Copeland (8)'''|'''Draw 2'''\n||{{flagicon|USA}} Jack May (4)|L|{{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Alex Nicholson (fighter)|Alex Nicholson]] (5)'''|'''TKO 1'''\n||{{flagicon|BRA}} '''[[Philipe Lins]] (3)'''|'''SUB 1'''|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Caio Alencar]]* (9)|L\n||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kelvin Tiller]] (2)|L|{{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Jared Rosholt]] (7)'''|'''UD 2'''\n<!-- semi finals -->\n||{{flagicon|USA}} '''Josh Copeland (8)'''|'''KO 1'''|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Alex Nicholson (fighter)|Alex Nicholson]] (5)|L\n||{{flagicon|BRA}} '''[[Philipe Lins]] (3)'''|'''TKO 2'''|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jared Rosholt]] (7)|L\n<!-- final -->\n||{{flagicon|USA}} Josh Copeland (8)|L|{{flagicon|BRA}} '''[[Philipe Lins]] (3)'''|'''TKO 4'''\n||||RD4=Final}}\n\n''* Valdrin Istrefi was originally scheduled to face Philipe Lins but was forced to pull out of the bout. He was replaced by Caio Alencar.\n\n{| style=\"border:1px solid black;\" align=left\n|+ '''Legend'''\n|-\n| style=\"width:60px;\" | <center>(SD)</center>\n| &nbsp;\n| (Split Decision)\n|-\n| style=\"width:60px;\" | <center>(UD)</center>\n| &nbsp;\n| (Unanimous Decision)\n|-\n| style=\"width:60px;\" | <center>(MD)</center>\n| &nbsp;\n| (Majority Decision)\n|-\n| style=\"width:60px;\" | <center>