ts}}\n{{2018 in mixed martial arts}}\n\n[[Category:Professional Fighters League]]\n[[Category:2018 in mixed martial arts]]\n[[Category:Mixed martial arts in New Orleans]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in New Orleans]]\n[[Category:October 2018 sports events in the United States]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Professional Fighters League MMA event in 2018}}\n{{Infobox MMA event\n|name=PFL 8\n|promotion=[[Professional Fighters League]]\n|date= {{start date|2018|10|05}}\n|venue= [[Ernest N. Morial Convention Center]]\n|city= [[New Orleans, Louisiana]]\n|attendance= \n|previousevent=[[PFL 7 (2018 season)|PFL 7]]\n|followingevent=[[PFL 9 (2018 season)|PFL 9]]\n}}\n\nThe '''''PFL 8''''' [[mixed martial arts]] event for the 2018 season of the [[Professional Fighters League]] was held on October 5, 2018, at the [[Ernest N. Morial Convention Center]] in [[New Orleans, Louisiana]].<ref name=\"PFL8\">{{Cite web|url=https://mmajunkie.com/2018/08/playoff-matchups-set-for-pfls-first-season-of-1-million-winners/2|title=Playoff matchups set for PFL's first season of $1 million winners|publisher=mmajunkie.com|author=Staff|date=2018-08-31|access-date=2018-08-31}}</ref>\n\n==Background==\nThe event was the eighth of the 2018 season and marked the start of the playoffs.<ref name=\"PFL8\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://pflmma.com/nola|title=Fight Card - PFL 8|publisher=PFL}}</ref>\n\n[[Philipe Lins]] was expected to face Valdrin Istrefi in a playoff bout at this event, however, Istrefi was removed due to injury and replaced by the highest ranked alternate on the undercard, [[Caio Alencar]]. As a result, Alencar's original opponent of [[Mike Kyle]] was paired with Mo De'Reese in a bout to determine a new alternate.\n\n[[Timur Valiev]] was expected to face Alexandre de Almeida in a playoff bout at this event, however, Valiev was removed due to injury and replaced by the highest ranked alternate on the undercard, [[Jumabieke Tuerxun]]. As a result, Tuerxun's original opponent of [[Marcos Galv\u00e3o]] was set to face [[Jeremy Kennedy]] in a bout to determine a new alternate. However, on the day of the event Kennedy dropped out due to undisclosed reasons, and so Galvao was automatically pushed forward as the new alternate instead.\n\n==Fight card==\n{{MMAevent}}\n{{MMAevent card|Main Card (NBCSN)}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|Josh Copeland\n|def.\n|[[Alex Nicholson (fighter)|Alex Nicholson]]\n|KO (punch)\n|1\n|1:27\n|Semi-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Featherweight\n|[[Steven Siler]]\n|def.\n|Alexandre Almeida\n|DQ (illegal upkick)\n|2\n|0:52\n|Semi-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Featherweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|[[Philipe Lins]]\n|def.\n|[[Jared Rosholt]]\n|TKO (punches)\n|2\n|0:45\n|Semi-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Featherweight\n|[[Lance Palmer]]\n|def.\n|[[Andre Harrison]]\n|Decision (unanimous) (30-27, 29-28, 29-28) \n|3\n|5:00\n|Semi-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Featherweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|Josh Copeland\n|vs.\n|[[Francimar Barroso]]\n|Draw (unanimous) (19-19, 19-19, 19-19)\n|2\n|5:00\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Featherweight\n|[[Steven Siler]]\n|def.\n|[[Nazareno Malegarie]]\n|Draw (majority) (20-18, 19-19, 19-19)\n|2\n|5:00\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Featherweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent card|Preliminary card (Facebook Watch)|header=no}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|[[Alex Nicholson (fighter)|Alex Nicholson]]\n|def.\n|Jack May\n|TKO (leg kick and punches)\n|1\n|2:03\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Heavyweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Featherweight\n|Alexandre Almeida\n|def.\n|[[Jumabieke Tuerxun]]\n|Decision (majority) (20-18, 20-18, 19-19)\n|2\n|5:00\n|Quarter-final round bout of the 2018 PFL Featherweight playoffs.\n}}\n{{MMAevent bout\n|Heavyweight\n|[[Philipe Lins]]\n