r]].\n\n==Career==\nPeppe began his senior career at [[Defensor Sporting]] in 2002, moving to [[Club Sportivo Cerrito|Cerrito]] in 2005. He signed for [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]] in 2007.\n\nHe made his international debut for [[Andorra national football team|Andorra]] in 2011.\n\n==External links==\n*{{NFT player|pid=45157}}\n*{{UEFA player|1903307}}\n*[https://www.lapreferente.com/J221079/fc-encamp/edu-peppe.html Edu Peppe] at La Preferente\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2011}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Peppe, Carlos}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Montevideo]]\n[[Category:Uruguayan emigrants to Andorra]]\n[[Category:Andorran people of Uruguayan descent]]\n[[Category:Andorran footballers]]\n[[Category:Andorra international footballers]]\n[[Category:Defensor Sporting players]]\n[[Category:Sportivo Cerrito players]]\n[[Category:UE Sant Juli\u00e0 players]]\n[[Category:FC Andorra players]]\n[[Category:FC Encamp players]]\n[[Category:UE Engordany players]]\n[[Category:Primera Divisi\u00f3 players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Spain]]\n\n{{Andorra-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name          = Carlos Peppe\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Carlos Eduardo Peppe Britos\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1983|1|28|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Montevideo]], Uruguay\n| height         = {{Convert|1.71|m|0|abbr=on}}\n| position       = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub    = [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]]\n| clubnumber     = 4\n| years1         = 2002&ndash;2004 | clubs1         = [[Defensor Sporting]] | caps1          =  | goals1         = \n| years2         = 2005&ndash;2006 | clubs2         = [[Club Sportivo Cerrito|Cerrito]] | caps2          = 37 | goals2         = 0\n| years3         = 2007&ndash;2014 | clubs3         = [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]] | caps3          =  | goals3         = \n| years4         = 2014&ndash;2015 | clubs4         = [[FC Andorra]] | caps4          = 38 | goals4         = 3\n| years5         = 2015&ndash;2016 | clubs5         = [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]] | caps5          = 17 | goals5         = 1\n| years6         = 2016&ndash;2017 | clubs6         = [[FC Encamp|Encamp]] | caps6          = 25 | goals6         = 2\n| years7         = 2017&ndash;2019 | clubs7         = [[UE Engordany|Engordany]] | caps7          = 44 | goals7         = 0\n| years8         = 2019&ndash;     | clubs8         = [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]] | caps8          = 13 | goals8         = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2011&ndash;\n| nationalteam1  = [[Andorra national football team|Andorra]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 21\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| club-update    = 21:25, 10 February 2020 (UTC)\n| ntupdate       = 10 October 2015\n}}\n'''Carlos Eduardo \"Edu\" Peppe Britos''' (born 28 January 1983) is an [[Uruguay]]an-born [[Andorra]]n international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0]] in [[Primera Divisi\u00f3]], as a [[midfielder]].\n\n==Career==\nPeppe began his senior career at [[Defensor Sporting]] in 2002, moving to [[Club Sportivo Cerrito|Cerrito]] in 2005. He signed for [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]] in 2007.\n\nHe made his international debut for [[Andorra national football team|Andorra]] in 2011.\n\n==External links==\n*{{NFT player|pid=45157}}\n*{{UEFA player|1903307}}\n*[https://www.lapreferente.com/J221079/fc-encamp/edu-peppe.html Edu Peppe] at La Preferente\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2011}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Peppe, Carlos}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Montevideo]]\n[[Category:Uruguayan emigrants to Andorra]]\n[[Category:Andorran people of Uruguayan descent]]\n[[Category:Andorran footballers]]\n[[Category:Andorra international footballers]]\n[[Category:Defensor Sporting players]]\n[[Category:Sportivo Cerrito players]]\n[[Category:UE Sant Juli\u00e0 players]]\n[[Category:FC Andorra players]]\n[[Category:FC Encamp players]]\n[[Category:UE Engordany players]]\n[[Category:Primera Divisi\u00f3 players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Spain]]\n\n{{Andorra-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Uruguayan-born Andorran footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Peppe"}
